text: The Canal de Meaux à Chalifert is a canal in northern France connecting the Marne River at Meaux to the Marne at Chalifert. At Lesches there is a canal tunnel. ==See also== * List of canals in France ==References== ==External links== * Project Babel Meaux Category:Canals opened in 1846
title: Canal de Meaux à Chalifert
